                                </p>
                            </div>
                            <div className="space-y-3 pt-3 mt-3 border-t border-gray-600">
                                <div>
                                    <label className="text-white font-medium block mb-1 text-sm">OpenAI API Key</label>
                                    <input 
                                        type="password" 
                                        value={openAIKey} 
                                        onChange={(e) => setOpenAIKey(e.target.value)}
                                        placeholder="sk-..." 
